rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0030
rows.name: though the time to me was meaningless.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0050
rows.name: Then we'll try to make this quick.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0080
rows.name:
I had thought by pitting myself against you,
I may understand death.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0100
rows.name:
At this late juncture,
it may be that I am no longer even your enemy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0110
rows.name: Since the conflict is in itself meaningless.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0140
rows.name: You should know that your "contest" has cost me my home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0150
rows.name: I've been nursing a hell of a grudge.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0160
rows.name:
But now, I've resolved to put my life 
on the line and fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0170
rows.name: If you make threats against our very existence...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0175
rows.name: and stand in the way of our will to live...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0185
rows.name: I'm prepared to end you, if it's the last thing I do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0220
rows.name: Why don't you TRY to understand?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0230
rows.name:
If you're as smart as you think,
you should be more than able to![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0240
rows.name: It is not a question of my ability.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0260
rows.name:
As I have stated, my actions are automatic,
dictated by necessity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0290
rows.name: I am the prime intellect of Samaar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0300
rows.name: Gaps in my knowledge are impermissible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0330
rows.name: Is it simply...nothing more than the price of defeat?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0340
rows.name: Does it express the ending of existence?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0350
rows.name: But then, how should one define your kind's existence, exactly?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0380
rows.name:
Not the abyss at the heart of everything,
where all consciousness has accumulated.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0390
rows.name:
You are ignorant... Even of the art of sealing
a mind within a person-shaped effigy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0400
rows.name:
Ignorant that you have made nothing more
than an artificial recreation of its structure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0410
rows.name: Wait, what was that about an abyss...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0420
rows.name: So it's true, there really is something else.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0430
rows.name: It's not just the Lifehold that holds our minds...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0440
rows.name:
And mimeosome tech...
It was just copying something else?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0470
rows.name: Chance has its hand in all things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0480
rows.name:
It was by pure blind chance that you successfully
tapped into the universal abyss, even fractionally.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0490
rows.name: For that, I must commend you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0500
rows.name: That is precisely what makes you so comical.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0530
rows.name:
How fallow your understanding,
with your meager intellectual ability...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0560
rows.name: I say death isn't the end.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0580
rows.name: It's just the end of the organic process.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0670
rows.name: But you are at your limit...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0675
rows.name: You accept what you have understood and no more.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0690
rows.name: The only due consideration is death.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0730
rows.name: It looks to me like you're just running away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0760
rows.name: Escape is much more active than acceptance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0780
rows.name: I will ensure my existence alone will win out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0810
rows.name: If death is the price for losing,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0870
rows.name: There is an obvious fact on display here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0910
rows.name: There is naught in all existence I cannot learn.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0930
rows.name: That right there is the proof of your ignorance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0940
rows.name: You don't even know that you don't know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0950
rows.name: And since you're unable to accept that truth...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0960
rows.name: You just went and declared yourself the loser![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0980
rows.name:
Forthwith, I will mete out your death.
And in victory...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33140100_MSG0990
rows.name: I shall transcend this insufferable world.[ST:wait ]
